                "NIST Control Description": "a. Enable authorized users to determine whether access authorizations assigned to a sharing partner match the information\u2019s access and use restrictions for [Assignment: organization-defined information sharing circumstances where user discretion is required]; and\n b. Employ [Assignment: organization-defined automated mechanisms or manual processes] to assist users in making information sharing and collaboration decisions.",
